STX Pan Ocean Says Leak Found on Mega-Ship Vale Beijing at Brazilian Port

-- B y   K y u n g h e e   P a r k
-- 
2011-12-05T08:53:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-05/stx-pan-ocean-says-leak-found-on-mega-ship-vale-beijing-at-brazilian-port.html
STX Pan Ocean Co. said a leak was
found in a ballast tank on the Vale Beijing while cargo was
being loaded onto the vessel.  The South Korean company is looking into the cause and plans
to move the ship for repairs, it said in an e-mailed response to
Bloomberg. The leak was first reported by the O Globo newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kyunghee Park at 
 kpark3@bloomberg.net  